data.description: This gorgeous home welcomes you the minute you step inside. Grand 10'' ceilings, engineered hardwood foyer, formal dining room and kitchen flooring. The spacious family room features a gas log fireplace, surrounded by beautiful custom built cabinetry. The kitchen is every cooks dream, complete with tall kitchen cabinets, granite counter tops, upgraded appliances, gas stove, snack bar and breakfast nook. The formal dining room boasts a coffered ceiling, wanes coating and chair rail. This lovely split floor plan offers master bedroom privacy and ample sized secondary bedrooms. The lavish master bath features a garden tub and separate shower. Upstairs you''ll find an enormous finished bonus room, and a huge storage room! Last but not least, you''ll love the beautiful screened in porch, grilling patio and fully privacy fenced yard. This home has it all!
